name: Camtasia Studio Asset Information File
summary: Learn about .ASSETPROJ files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: An ASSETPROJ file is commonly contained in a .LIBZIP file, which is used by Camtasia Studio to share library media. You can download content such as themes, intro assets, callouts, and SuperStamps assets.
NOTE: The ASSETPROJ file is located in the Asset folder.

description: File used by Camtasia Studio, a screen recording and video editing program; stores asset information referenced by Camtasia Studio.
